705311f-a.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - 91st Street (East)
705311f-a.text:
9025 King's Highway, at the N.W. corner of East 91st Street, show-
ing the home of P. Siglock in 1873 and John Siglock in 1923. This
house is standing about a century. Shown on the left, are the rears
of buildings on the west side of East 91st Street.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
The same, showing in the foreground, the fill for King'a Highway.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
